{"data":[{"date":"14:42 01/07","title":"Ch\u1ed1t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Arsenal c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/chot-thoi-diem-arsenal-cong-bo-tan-binh-25-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Arsenal mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Lucas Torreira t\u1eeb Sampdoria, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 7 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal \u0111ang \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n Lucas Torreira</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRamsey ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2019 nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Jack Wilshere ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do. HLV Unai Emery bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Lucas Torreira v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Arsenal mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Lucas Torreira v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/13/chot-thoi-diem-arsenal-cong-bo-tan-binh-25-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Lucas Torreira\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLucas Torreira c\u1ee7a Sampdoria l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Arsenal nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia. Ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n khi t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua Torreira \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1edbi 36 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Serie A v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Anh l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Italia \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, h\u1ecd \u0111ang \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Sampdoria x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1eafp b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Uruguay \u1edf World Cup 2018, anh c\u0169ng tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt. R\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay, Lucas Torreira khi\u1ebfn\u00a0Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/neville-khen-ngoi-tan-binh-arsenal-sau-tran-uruguay-vs-bo-dao-nha-469-190073.html\" target=\"_blank\">Gary Neville khen Lucas Torreira</span>, c\u1ef1u sao M.U \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996, Gary Neville tin r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay t\u1edbi Emirates, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Arsenal s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal s\u1ebd c\u00f3 Torreira v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 7 n\u00e0y</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Lucas Torreira t\u1eeb Sampdoria, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal chieu mo Torreira voi gia 30 trieu euro\" title=\"Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Torreira v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/13/chu-tich-sampdoria-xac-nhan-ban-sao-khung-cho-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal s\u1ebd c\u00f3 Lucas Torreira v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 7 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, hai b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n ch\u1edd c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Arsenal.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nUruguay s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 6 th\u00e1ng 7, Torreira l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"785","checkdouble":"190091"},{"date":"14:58 01/07","title":"Liverpool \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Karius","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/28/liverpool-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai-karius.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Loris Karius g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh, theo \u0111\u00f3 anh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Klopp ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Loris Karius</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLoris Karius l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Klopp \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c mang v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Simon Mignolet.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Loris Karius \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Klopp quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Loris Karius \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Klopp quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/27/Tuong-lai-Loris-Karius-duoc-HLV-Klopp-quyet-dinh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Klopp ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Karius</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh Karius \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1eadt Mignolet \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c trong khung g\u1ed7. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft C1\u00a02018 v\u1edbi Real Madrid, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf 2/3 b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a Liverpool, khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-3. Sau nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda n\u00e0y Karius g\u1eb7p \u00e1p l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, kh\u00f4ng \u00edt ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool n\u00ean t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c Liverpool s\u1ebd mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n gi\u1ecfi \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed The Kop c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra t\u1edbi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, theo The Sun v\u00e0 ESPN, HLV Klopp s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i trong khung g\u1ed7 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, theo \u0111\u00f3 Karius ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a The Kop \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng theo ESPN, HLV Klopp s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf v\u00e0i ch\u1ee5c tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao nh\u01b0 Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma hay Courtois c\u1ee7a Chelsea.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson\" title=\"Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/24/liverpool-chap-nhan-that-bai-vu-thu-mon-79-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool kh\u00f4ng mua Alisson \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/day-muc-tieu-so-1-cua-liverpool-o-he-2018-172-181789.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m Jack Butland</span> c\u1ee7a Stoke City, song th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bet365.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Liverpool kh\u00f4ng mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Mignolet s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i Anfield. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"784","checkdouble":"190092"},{"date":"15:09 01/07","title":"T\u00e2n binh Politano n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi gia nh\u1eadp Inter?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/politano-phat-bieu-ve-inter-clb-moi-gia-nhap.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Dele Alli ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dele Alli tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Dele Alli d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00f9i. Ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Tottenham ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n \u1edf ph\u00fat 80 v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho Ruben Loftus-Cheek.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Colombia, Dele Alli ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Colombia, Dele Alli ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/dele-alli-len-tieng-ve-kha-nang-ra-san-truoc-colombia.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Dele Alli \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i khi\u1ebfn Alli kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh v\u1edbi Panama v\u00e0 B\u1ec9. NHM Tam s\u01b0 \u0111ang lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Colombia \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t Dele Alli ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u1ed5n sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f9ng Anh gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ec1 ra\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Dele Alli ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 Steven Gerrard</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Colombia, Dele Alli c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 v\u1edbi huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Liverpool, Steven Gerrard.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alli DT Anh\" title=\"Alli \u0110T Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/dele-alli-bay-cach-giup-dt-anh-thanh-cong-o-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alli ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 Steven Gerrard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cAnh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, t\u00f4i ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Gerrard t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf. L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1edfi t\u1eeb anh \u1ea5y, \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cTinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Gerrard c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 m\u00e0 t\u00f4i ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9, anh \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng ch\u1ea1y khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u01b0a k\u1ebft th\u00fac. Gerrard l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1eabu m\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Liverpool\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAnh \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i s\u00e2u \u1edf World Cup 2018, n\u1ebfu v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Colombia \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n ho\u1eb7c Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. V\u1edbi nh\u00e1nh thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 Tam s\u01b0 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t s\u00e1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/neu-khong-vao-ban-ket-anh-se-co-mot-ky-world-cup-that-bai-421-190002.html\" target=\"_blank\">Paul Merson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh</span>, c\u1ef1u sao Arsenal kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Tam s\u01b0 s\u1ebd th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf World Cup 2018 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o top 4 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"783","checkdouble":"190095"},{"date":"15:30 01/07","title":"Napoli quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/7/20/hlv-conte-khang-dinh-ngung-theo-duoi-koulibaly.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Kalidou Koulibaly ho\u1eb7c Dries Mertens c\u1ee7a Napoli, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u00f4i sao cho The Blues.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Napoli nh\u1ea3 Sarri cho Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, HLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u1ed9t ng\u1ed9t r\u1eddi Napoli d\u00f9 v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Carlo Ancelotti, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec9nh cao.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Napoli h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Napoli h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/31/Chuyen-nhuong-Chelsea-2018-gap-kho-vu-sao-khung-Napoli-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Maurizio Sarri s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m thay Conte</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n gi\u1eefa Sarri v\u00e0 Napoli, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ra 6 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n San Paolo.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a HLV Sarri v\u1ec1 thay Conte, ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. C\u1ef1u HLV Juventus kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap The Blues c\u00f3 v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, ngo\u00e0i ra \u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, Chelsea s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c sa th\u1ea3i Conte v\u00e0 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri trong \u00edt gi\u1edd t\u1edbi, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f4ng qua nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n v\u1edbi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Napoli s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 sao kh\u1ee7ng cho Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Kalidou Koulibaly ho\u1eb7c Dries Mertens c\u1ee7a Napoli, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u00f4i sao cho The Blues.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"koulibaly\" title=\"koulibaly\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/9/20/muc-tieu-cua-chelsea-gia-han-voi-napoli-them-5-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Napoli s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 Koulibaly cho Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Mirror kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Napoli ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 Sarri t\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ee9 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 Kalidou Koulibaly ho\u1eb7c Dries Mertens th\u00ec h\u1ecd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i l\u00e0m n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Ancelotti.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/trung-ve-nay-khien-chelsea-phai-chi-65-trieu-bang-o-he-2018-172-184925.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Koulibaly</span>, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal thay Gary Cahill, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Mertens \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafm thay v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Morata.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Napoli ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNapoli c\u0169ng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Jorginho cho Man City, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Man xanh d\u00e0nh cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"782","checkdouble":"190096"},{"date":"15:42 01/07","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! B\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Martial n\u1ebfu r\u1eddi MU?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/14/day-ben-do-moi-cua-martial-neu-roi-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Bayern Munich mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p r\u1eddi Old Trafford nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Martial tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nong-tien-dao-martial-tuyen-bo-chia-tay-mu-172-188440.html\" target=\"_blank\">Anthony Martial tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u1eddi MU</span>, theo \u0111\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bayern Munich mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Bayern Munich mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/day-ben-do-moi-cua-martial-neu-roi-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Martial s\u1ebd d\u1ee9t \u00e1o chia tay MU h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Alexis Sanchez ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, anh kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed Martial c\u00f2n x\u1ebfp sau Rashford trong vai tr\u00f2 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Sanchez.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean khi\u1ebfn Martial b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Ph\u00e1p d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018, \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng \u01b0u ti\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u. B\u1edfi v\u1eady c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ee9t \u00e1o ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i, \u1edf Anh Chelsea, Liverpool v\u00e0 Tottenham ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ef1u sao Monaco. B\u00ean ngo\u00e0i bi\u00ean gi\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, Juventus, Bayern v\u00e0 PSG c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Bayern s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Martial v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 75 tri\u1ec7u euro</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bayern Munich mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p r\u1eddi Old Trafford nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\"><br>\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Martial chiem tron mat bao trong lan dau ra mat\" title=\"Martial chi\u1ebfm tr\u1ecdn m\u1eb7t b\u00e1o trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ra m\u1eaft\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/24/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-hom-nay-ngay-156,-tin-nong-chuyen-nhuong-he-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bayern b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Martial\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nDaily Star kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Bayern \u0111\u00e3 \u00e2m th\u1ea7m g\u1eb7p ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Martial, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c M.U b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995, Bayern ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 75 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Martial n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, \u00f4ng c\u0169ng \u0111ang nh\u1eafm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995. Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"781","checkdouble":"190097"},{"date":"15:51 01/07","title":"Dele Alli l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/dele-alli-len-tieng-ve-kha-nang-ra-san-truoc-colombia.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Dele Alli ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dele Alli tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Dele Alli d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00f9i. Ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Tottenham ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n \u1edf ph\u00fat 80 v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho Ruben Loftus-Cheek.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Colombia, Dele Alli ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Colombia, Dele Alli ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/dele-alli-len-tieng-ve-kha-nang-ra-san-truoc-colombia.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Dele Alli \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i khi\u1ebfn Alli kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh v\u1edbi Panama v\u00e0 B\u1ec9. NHM Tam s\u01b0 \u0111ang lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Colombia \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t Dele Alli ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u1ed5n sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f9ng Anh gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ec1 ra\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Dele Alli ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 Steven Gerrard</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Colombia, Dele Alli c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 v\u1edbi huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Liverpool, Steven Gerrard.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alli DT Anh\" title=\"Alli \u0110T Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/dele-alli-bay-cach-giup-dt-anh-thanh-cong-o-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alli ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 Steven Gerrard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cAnh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, t\u00f4i ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Gerrard t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf. L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1edfi t\u1eeb anh \u1ea5y, \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cTinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Gerrard c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 m\u00e0 t\u00f4i ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9, anh \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng ch\u1ea1y khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u01b0a k\u1ebft th\u00fac. Gerrard l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1eabu m\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Liverpool\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAnh \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i s\u00e2u \u1edf World Cup 2018, n\u1ebfu v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Colombia \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n ho\u1eb7c Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. V\u1edbi nh\u00e1nh thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 Tam s\u01b0 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t s\u00e1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/neu-khong-vao-ban-ket-anh-se-co-mot-ky-world-cup-that-bai-421-190002.html\" target=\"_blank\">Paul Merson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh</span>, c\u1ef1u sao Arsenal kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Tam s\u01b0 s\u1ebd th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf World Cup 2018 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o top 4 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"780","checkdouble":"190098"},{"date":"16:09 01/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u00e1ng t\u01b0\u01a1i cho tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u s\u1edbm T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Nga","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/truc-tiep-nga-vs-tay-ban-nha.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Nga \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u1eeb lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng 1/8 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua. Ch\u00fang ta h\u00e3y rung \u0111\u00f9i v\u00e0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u00f9ng nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-nga-vs-tay-ban-nha-463-190102.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/truc-tiep-nga-vs-tay-ban-nha.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-nga-vs-tay-ban-nha-463-190102.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Nga 21h00 ng\u00e0y 1/7 (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Nga vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Nga v\u00f2ng 1/8 16 \u0111\u1ed9i World Cup 2018 l\u00fac...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- <strong>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (\u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3)<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: T\u00e2y Ban Nha th\u1eafng 2-1<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u:</em> T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Nga<br>\r\n<em>Th\u1eddi gian:</em> 21h ng\u00e0y 1/7<br>\r\n<em>\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m: </em>S\u00e2n Luzhniki<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>TLCA c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn:</em> T\u00e2y Ban Nha -0.95*0:1*0.90 Nga<br>\r\n<em>TBT c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: </em>Nhi\u1ec1u 0.96*2 1/2*0.97 \u00cdt<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Nga v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, soi k\u00e8o, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Nga v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, soi k\u00e8o, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/nhan-dinh-tay-ban-nha-vs-nga-va-du-doan-soi-keo-tbn-vs-nga.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Nga 21h ng\u00e0y 1/7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, ai c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c, d\u00f9 ti\u1ebft t\u1ea5u c\u00f3 nhanh hay ch\u1eadm, n\u00f3 c\u0169ng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n 3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1edbi rung v\u1edbi 2 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Uruguay. C\u00f2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Argentina 4-3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Nga b\u1ecb t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf b\u1edfi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. V\u1ed1n d\u0129 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c tho\u00e1ng h\u01a1n Uruguay, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u00fd g\u00ec kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. V\u1edbi Nga, &ldquo;b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t th\u1eadt&rdquo; c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 r\u00f5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Suarez chuyen bong cho Cavani ghi ban\" title=\"Suarez chuyen bong cho Cavani ghi ban\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/Du-am-Uruguay-2-1-Bo-Dao-Nha-Ronaldo-ghen-ti-voi-Suarez-&ndash;-Cavani-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u0169ng c\u00f3 3 b\u00e0n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n2 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Saudi Arabia v\u00e0 Ai C\u1eadp qu\u00e1 y\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Nga ph\u1ea3i \u00e2u lo. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t Uruguay ngay c\u1ea3 khi ch\u01a1i c\u1ea7m ch\u1eebng v\u1eabn khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd \u00f4m h\u1eadn v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn thua 3 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1. Nga v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 nh\u00e0 v\u1eabn v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7y h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n song \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7y l\u1ecfng l\u1ebbo \u1edf h\u1eadu ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLi\u00ean ti\u1ebfp l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 Nga ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Uruguay. 3 b\u00e0n thua v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u01a1i \u00edt n\u1ebfu bi\u1ebft &ldquo;Nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa g\u1ea5u&rdquo; \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i g\u1ed3ng m\u00ecnh ch\u1ecbu 16 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ee7 lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, s\u1ee9c \u00e9p t\u1eeb T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1ea1o ra tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nga h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea3m \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nga that bai tui ho 0-3\" title=\"Nga that bai tui ho 0-3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Nga-that-bai-tui-ho-0-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nga b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn thua Uruguay</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Nga. N\u00f3 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 k\u00e9m v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Ngay trong khung g\u1ed7, David de Gea d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc t\u1ea1i Man United.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng l\u00ean \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha, De Gea th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c theo chi\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c. Ph\u00eda tr\u00ean th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 b\u1ecb t\u00e2m l\u00fd, b\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 v\u1ec7 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 y\u00ean t\u00e2m. 4 trong s\u1ed1 5 b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a TBN t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n (2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ma R\u1ed1c).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Boutaid ha guc De Gea cua TBN\" title=\"Boutaid ha guc De Gea cua TBN\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/HLV-Hierro-phat-bieu-sau-tran-TBN-2-2-Ma-Roc-voi-su-lo-au-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u01b0ng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. V\u1eabn thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng, v\u1eabn g\u1ed3m nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, song ch\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn La Roja g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 trong ch\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng. Hai h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a TBN d\u00e2ng r\u1ea5t cao, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ed1t b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u01b0 Andres Iniesta hay David Silva.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede trung l\u1ed9, nh\u1eefng Sergio Ramos v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Gerard Pique ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p h\u01a1n. Vi\u1ec7c v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Pique gi\u1edd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00f4 danh c\u1ee7a Iran hay Ma R\u1ed1c c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tay-ban-nha-run-ray-buoc-tiep-voi-nhung-cau-hoi-khong-duoc-tra-loi-421-190085.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/tay-ban-nha-run-ray-buoc-tiep-voi-nhung-cau-hoi-khong-duoc-tra-loi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tay-ban-nha-run-ray-buoc-tiep-voi-nhung-cau-hoi-khong-duoc-tra-loi-421-190085.html\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha: Run r\u1ea9y b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi</span><br>\r\n<span>M\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 2-3 tu\u1ea7n g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e2y th\u00f4i nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00fang v\u1eady, ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018 th\u00ec c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c Julen Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t k\u00e9m. V\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n sau khi HLV Julen Lopetegui b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i, Fernando Hierro ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft r\u1ed1t r\u00e1o. Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Nga tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u thay \u0111\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ea5t s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 mang tin vui t\u1edbi v\u1edbi Nga. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u01a1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta ngh\u0129. V\u00e0 h\u1ecd t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c l\u00e0m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi TBN trong \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i Luzhniki t\u1ed1i ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt n\u00e0y (1/7).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Hierro\" title=\"HLV Hierro\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/hlv-hierro-phat-bieu-sau-tran-tbn-22-ma-roc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Hierro ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap TBN kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e2y Ban Nha thua 2 b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh, Nga \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Aleksandr Golovin th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t &ldquo;b\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft&rdquo;. \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u00ednh \u0111\u00f2n ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ma R\u1ed1c, Nga \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Denis Cheryshev r\u1ea5t nhanh v\u00e0 tr\u1ef1c di\u1ec7n. TBN th\u1ee7ng 1 b\u00e0n t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ma R\u1ed1c, \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 &ldquo;t\u00f2a th\u00e1p&rdquo; Artem Dzyuba.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, c\u1ea3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 Nga \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. V\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. C\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c 2,5 tr\u00e1i m\u00e0 gi\u1edbi d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u1eb7t ra cho m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i gi\u1eefa TBN v\u00e0 Nga nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd s\u1edbm b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh s\u1eadp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- <strong>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng </strong>(\u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3)<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: T\u00e2y Ban Nha th\u1eafng 2-1<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00e1c:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng l\u1eafm l\u00e0 9 (U 9 1/2)<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 5 (O 4 1/2)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Nga s\u1ebd nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n (-3/4)<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 4 (O 4)<br>\r\n- S\u1ebd xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t trong hi\u1ec7p 1 (O 1)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLong Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"779","checkdouble":"190099"},{"date":"16:36 01/07","title":"Maradona: \u201cArgentina b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 phim ch\u1ebft ch\u00f3c\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/maradona-phat-bieu-ve-dt-argentina-bi-loai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Diego Maradona ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Argentina v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ng\u00e1n ng\u1ea9m. Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 x\u1ee9 Tango kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 phim n\u01a1i bi\u00ean ni\u00ean s\u1eed v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i ch\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Argentina b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArgentina kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7 \u1edf \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 Antoine Griezmann \u0111\u01b0a Les Bleus v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc r\u1ed3i h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. May m\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi th\u00eam trong hi\u1ec7p 1, Argentina c\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a Angel Di Maria tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u1eabn 2-1 nh\u1edd c\u00fa ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng may m\u1eafn c\u1ee7a Gabriel Mercado.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 mong manh c\u1ee7a Argentina kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. Benjamin Pavard l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m, Kylian Mbappe l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap gi\u00fap \u201cG\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng\u201d t\u1ea1o c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 4-2. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng mu\u1ed9n c\u1ee7a Sergio Aguero kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 gi\u00fap Argentina tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi tr\u1eadn thua 3-4 chung cu\u1ed9c v\u00e0 d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Maradona ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Argentina v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ng\u00e1n ng\u1ea9m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Maradona ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Argentina v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ng\u00e1n ng\u1ea9m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/maradona-phat-bieu-ve-dt-argentina-bi-loai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Maradona ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Argentina v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ng\u00e1n ng\u1ea9m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Maradona kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDiego Maradona, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup v\u1edbi Argentina n\u0103m 1986 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi tin r\u1eb1ng k\u1ebft c\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a La Albiceleste \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn r\u1ea1p chi\u1ebfu phim nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n b\u00f3ng. Ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ec3 xem bi\u00ean ni\u00ean s\u1eed c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i ch\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra\u201d, Maradona ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Argentina sau tr\u1eadn thua Ph\u00e1p. \u201cPh\u00e1p phong t\u1ecfa Messi, h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Argentina. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i ph\u00eda sau h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Messi nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra theo \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n. Kh\u00f4ng mong \u0111\u1ee3i, nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 c\u0169ng x\u1ea3y ra. M\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup kh\u00e1c \u0111\u00e3 qua v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tay tr\u1eafng. Th\u1eadt t\u1ec7 khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t Argentina h\u1ed7n lo\u1ea1n t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Argentina tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/thua-phap-be-bang-javier-mascherano-chia-tay-dt-argentina-465-190042.html\">Thua Ph\u00e1p b\u1ebd b\u00e0ng, hai tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u00f9ng n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay \u0110T Argentina</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-diem-nhan-sau-tran-cau-sieu-kich-tinh-phap-43-argentina-421-190039.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u si\u00eau k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh Ph\u00e1p 4-3 Argentina</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/jorge-sampaoli-khong-tu-chuc-du-dt-argentina-bi-loai-465-190037.html\">Jorge Sampaoli kh\u00f4ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c d\u00f9 \u0110T Argentina b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-phap-43-argentina-421-190036.html\">4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 4-3 Argentina</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"778","checkdouble":"190100"},{"date":"17:06 01/07","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Nga 21h00 ng\u00e0y 1/7 (World Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/truc-tiep-nga-vs-tay-ban-nha.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Nga vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Nga v\u00f2ng 1/8 16 \u0111\u1ed9i World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 21h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 1/7.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Nga vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Nga v\u00f2ng 1/8 16 \u0111\u1ed9i World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 21h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 1/7.</h2>\r\nB\u1ecb l\u1ed7i, vui l\u00f2ng click t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-nga-vs-tay-ban-nha-463-190102.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP T\u00c2Y BAN NHA VS NGA</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"777","checkdouble":"190102"},{"date":